    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It honestly breaks my heart a little to even think about parting with this absolute gem, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014she\u2019s lived in a climate-controlled garage and honestly looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is deep and glossy, the interior still has that fresh scent, and she drives even smoother than she looks. There might be a microscopic speck of dust if you look with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s practically perfect. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a passion, you\u2019ve found it!",
